--
-- This procedure updates the customer photo validity date
-- for an existing customer profile.
--
-- The procedure is used when the submitted national identity
-- information matches the existing customer identity data
-- and no new photo inquiry is required.
--
-- The update operation refreshes the photo validity timestamp
-- using the current system date.
--
-- This procedure is part of the customer identity maintenance
-- and photo validation workflow.
